                    "(field) lsp.ClientCompletionItemOptions.labelDetailsSupport: boolean?",
                    "```",
                    "",
                    "---",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "The client has support for completion item label",
                    "details (see also `CompletionItemLabelDetails`).",
